pr_body:
- Enabled PostGIS to work with raster files
- Nominatim CLI tool can now import OSM views data when [osmviews.tiff](https://qrank.wmcloud.org/download/osmviews.tiff) is found in the `nominatim-project` directory
- Nominatim CLI tool can now refresh OSM views data and recompute the importance score with `nominatim refresh --osm-views --importance`
- Integrated OSM views data into the algorithm that computes the places' importance scores which are used in ranking Nominatim's search results
- Added some unit tests
- Updated the documentation and added a [report](https://github.com/tareqpi/Nominatim/blob/importance-by-osm-views/docs/gsoc22.md) of the experiments conducted about this PR
- Further investigation and testing are needed before merging this branch
